Julie Gayet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Julie_Gayet 0 Julie Gayet (French pronunciation: ​[ʒyli ɡajɛ]; born 3 June 1972) is a French film actress and film producer. She is also known for being the partner of the former President of the French Republic, François Hollande.
